### Motivation
- Introduce a repository-level policy that documents default instructions and constraints for AI agents collaborating in this repo and make a trivial cleanup in `walrus/walrus.cpp` to keep the tree tidy.

### Description
- Add `AGENTS.md` containing scope, collaboration mode, safety/change constraints, C++ editing conventions, validation guidance, and communication rules for AI agents.
- Remove a trailing blank/whitespace change in `walrus/walrus.cpp` (no functional changes).

### Testing
- No automated tests were run in this environment; smallest relevant checks could not be executed due to environment limitations.
